## Best Practices

### 1. Static Class Strings Only
```tsx
// ✅ JIT can analyze static strings
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2" />

// ❌ JIT can't analyze dynamic strings
<div className={`grid grid-cols-${cols}`} />
```

### 2. Use Semantic Breakpoints
```tsx
// ✅ Meaningful breakpoints
<div className="hidden md:block lg:hidden" />

// ❌ Avoid arbitrary breakpoints
<div className="md:w-[500px]" />
```

### 3. Combine with UI8Kit Components
```tsx
// ✅ Use Grid component for responsive grids
<Grid cols="1-2-3" gap="lg" />

// ✅ Use className for custom responsive behavior
<div className="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center" />
```

### 4. Performance Considerations
- Keep class strings short and focused
- Use component composition over complex class strings
- Prefer UI8Kit components for common patterns

